title: Dakine Omega Glove
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Omega Glove in our Rasta print.
Omega Features:
- Insert: Waterproof, windproof Polyurethane
- Insulation: High loft synthetic [ 80g ]
- Palm: Rubbertec
- Shell: Nylon / Poly with DWR treatment
- Lining: 230g fleece
- Cuff Closure: Zipper
- Nose wipe thumb panels
